BA2 — Cold Start onboarding. Structured belief-extraction questions, mirror moment, first-win output, background integration scan, portable onboarding via import, observed preference mechanism.
BA3 — Tiered presence as user permission. UI for a user to choose T1/T2/T3 engagement.
