Exit outcomes:

A new user, previously unknown to Hammerfall, successfully completes Cold Start and experiences Helm as meaningfully personal by the end of their first session
Multiple users are running concurrent independent Helms with verified data isolation
A user can change their tier setting (T1/T2/T3) and Helm's presence adjusts accordingly
